ear British kit if we were going to misbehave.\\\"\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9753368400619522, \"rank\": 0.02231982568569312, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pinsent's tweet came after Paris' closing ceremony descended into chaos on Sunday evening when athletes flooded onto the stage in their droves at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996291535, \"rank\": 3.7082292217081046e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They could be seen behind French band Phoenix during their performance.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9537475561387616, \"rank\": 0.04454813315067909, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9985053459102825, \"rank\": 0.0014857152968645497, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to theTelegraph, choreographer Thomas Jolly wanted them to surround the various platforms on the pitch, which were set out to represent the world map.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1135, \"end\": 1141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.999607553537203, \"rank\": 0.00026647283295872453, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The aim was to symbolise them taking \\\"possession of the world and its oceans\\\".\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in an apparent moment of miscommunication, they instead climbed up onto them.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An announcement was made over the PA system, twice in both French and English, urging: \\\"Dear athletes, please leave the stage.\\\"\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The situation was ultimately resolved after around 10 minutes, with stewards ushering the remaining athletes away.\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were not the only ones to invade the stage, however.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Notorious YouTube prankster Daniel Jarvis, known by his online alias 'Jarvo69',snuck into the ceremonydressed as a member of Team GB.\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notorious_(2009_film)\", \"score\": 0.5297039397374516, \"rank\": 0.543575745759507, \"text\": \"Notorious\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notorious_(2009_film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notorious_(2009_film)\"}, {\"begin\": 1739, \"end\": 1